OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride Cymru's
OL,4,Cbiggest ever event
OL,6,FAround 50,000 people took part in
OL,7,FPride Cymru in Cardiff over the
OL,8,Fweekend, making it the biggest
OL,9,Fattendance in the organisation's
OL,10,Fhistory.
OL,12,FThe event which champions the rights
OL,13,Fof LGBTQ+ people saw a parade meander
OL,14,Faround parts of the capital, followed
OL,15,Fby a festival within Cardiff Castle
OL,16,Fthat took place across the weekend.
OL,18,FRevellers were treated to performances
OL,19,Ffrom the likes of The Vengaboys,
OL,20,FUltrabeat, Heather Small and Scissor
OL,21,FSister's star Jake Shears.
