OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride Cymru's
OL,4,Cbiggest ever event
OL,6,FIt was a particularly special occasion
OL,7,Ffor Pride Cymru which celebrated its
OL,8,F25th anniversary having held its first
OL,9,Fevent in 1999.
OL,11,FBack then it was originally known as
OL,12,FMardi Gras, with a much more modest
OL,13,Fcrowd of 2,000 people attending to see
OL,14,Fcelebrations at Coopers Field in
OL,15,FCardiff's Bute Park.
OL,17,FFast forward a quarter of a century
OL,18,Fand Pride Cymru has now become an
OL,19,Fannual fixture within the city,
OL,20,Fdrawing in crowds from near and far.
