OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride Cymru's
OL,4,Cbiggest ever event
OL,6,F"We have people from Anglesey,
OL,7,FWrexham, Tenby, all areas. We've had
OL,8,Fpeople come from across the UK as far
OL,9,Fas Perth in Scotland, also people from
OL,10,Fthe United States, and the
OL,11,FNetherlands" said Dan Walsh, Vice
OL,12,FChair of Pride Cymru.
OL,14,F"Pride is all about coming together
OL,15,Fand finding your tribe, finding your
OL,16,Fchosen family. There are so many
OL,17,Fpeople that still feel isolated, 25
OL,18,Fyears after this event started.
