OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride Cymru's
OL,4,Cbiggest ever event
OL,6,F"It's a really important opportunity
OL,7,Fto celebrate how far we've come but
OL,8,Falso allow people to find a community
OL,9,Fthat loves them and that cares for
OL,10,Fthem."
OL,12,FCardiff Drag performer Rob Keetch,
OL,13,Falso known as Dr Bev, was at the
OL,14,Foriginal event.
OL,16,F"It was the first big event I'd been
OL,17,Fto performing as Dr Bev. Back then it
OL,18,Fwas just the 'Lesbian and Gay Mardi
OL,19,FGras'.
