OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride Cymru's
OL,4,Cbiggest ever event
OL,6,FFor Dr Bev, she says attitudes have
OL,7,Fchanged significantly in the last
OL,8,Fquarter of a century.
OL,10,F"I could walk through today in drag
OL,11,Fand people would be like 'uh ok',
OL,12,Fwhereas back then it would've been
OL,13,F'What is going on?!'."
OL,15,F"It's not just about the Pride event
OL,16,Fin Cardiff now. The world's biggest
OL,17,Fsmall film festival for LGBTQ people
OL,18,Fis held here in Cardiff. The Gay Games
OL,19,Fare coming here. We are really showing
OL,20,Fto the world, we are a small city but
OL,21,Fboy do we have a large voice!"
