OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride Cymru's
OL,4,Cbiggest ever event
OL,6,FEven though Pride has become a
OL,7,Fcelebration Dr Bev says it's still so
OL,8,Fmuch more than that.
OL,10,F"For me I look upon Pride in three
OL,11,Fdifferent ways: we celebrate how far
OL,12,Fwe've come, we commemorate those
OL,13,Fwho've walked that path for us and we
OL,14,Feducate those who still may not
OL,15,Frealise they are sewing seed of
OL,16,Fdiscomfort and hurt for others", she
OL,17,Fsaid.
